com.facebook.stats.mx

Interface StatType

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TemplateStatType

    public interface StatType
    String wrapper that can memoize and efficiently do prepend/append/INSERT For use with counters that need a default and a dynamic one (ex: per- category)

        StatType prepend(String prefix)

      • materialize

        StatType materialize(String value)
        will create StatType such that getKey() = prefix + value + suffix but leaves the internal prefix + suffix the same. ex: materialize("x").materialize("y").getKey() = prefix + "y" + suffix
        Parameters:
        value - - string to use as replacement value
        Returns:
        new StatType on which getKey() returns as specified
